title: Bug 121682: Exception thrown when exporting data from a table containing highlight/map
description: Exception is thrown when trying to export data from an attached report.
OB: When trying to export the data in the table, an exception is thrown in the ReportEngineService.getMetaData() method.
EB: The expected behavior is that the data should be exported successfully without any exceptions.
SR:
To reproduce the issue: 
1. Add a table to the report which contains a group, a highlight rule, and a map rule in the group row.
2. Preview the attached report.
3. Attempt to export the data from the table.
